ActImpact Assessment Act
PrecisReappointment of DAVID MCGOVERN of Ottawa, Ontario, as President of the Impact Assessment Agency of Canada on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until such time as a new President is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective August 28, 2020.
